section.t:
                    For example:



{
    "id": "http://example.com/root.json#",
    "definitions": {
        "schema1": { "id": "#foo" },
        "schema2": {
            "id": "other",
            "definitions": {
                "a": { "id": "#bar" },
                "b": { "id": "t/inner" }
            }
        },
        "schema3": {
            "id": "urn:uuid:ee564b8a-7a87-4125-8c96-e9f123d6766f"
        }
    }
}

The proposed MIME media type for JSON Schema is defined as follows:


    type name: application;
    subtype name: schema+json.

